{"tid":1396093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(全面開戰) 環球時報 : 中国不會再先考慮控制貿戰規模","createTime":"2019-08-02T03:35:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T05:26:30.000Z","uid":184679,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"aef4210dfe9bc9a8c0f8e4d892eafb3ee425599b","tid":1396093,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:35:07.000Z","msg":"大陸官媒「環球時報」總編輯胡錫進表示，中美貿易協議在「漸行漸遠」。<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進2日早上在Twitter發文指出，中國不會再優先考慮控制貿易戰規模，而是將關注貿易戰持續情況下的國家戰略。<br />\n<br />\n中美貿易代表31日結束在上海舉行的經貿高級別磋商，未見突破，惹來美國總統川普不滿，於2日凌晨約1時半，在Twitter宣布對餘下3,000億美元中國進口貨品加徵10％關稅，於9月1日生效。他又再次批評中國在談判時出爾反爾，亦沒有履行大量採購美國農產品的承諾。<br />\n<br />\n不過，川普同時表明，與中國的談判會繼續，期望能達成一份全面協議，又形容中美兩國合作前景光明。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://m.ctee.com.tw/livenews/lm/a06601002019080210353463?area=</code></pre>"},{"pid":"f326eaf9ab400108deee35ddbdc9f61cb067dfae","tid":1396093,"uid":15605,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:37:43.000Z","msg":"真係得侵呢啲生意人先可以將支那當狗咁撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"311080c607b601ac7374d0d2b1dbe9542f918e87","tid":1396093,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:41:43.000Z","msg":"香港多咗貴車里子<br />\n係未被屈要食QUOTA"},{"pid":"b1b1a2ee31543f752d79ccf6a63d355503348d2b","tid":1396093,"uid":69746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:43:06.000Z","msg":"合作前景一片光明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba839b661aa8853df3e7e95d983bab3f49b61cd2","tid":1396093,"uid":2429,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:43:14.000Z","msg":"川普同時表明，與中國的談判會繼續，期望能達成一份全面協議，又形容中美兩國合作前景光明。<br />\n<br />\n又撚。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2df29c354204f5f30eaed5f757a675a281cc9a33","tid":1396093,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"311080c607b601ac7374d0d2b1dbe9542f918e87","tid":1396093,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:41:43.000Z","msg":"香港多咗貴車里子<br />\n係未被屈要食QUOTA"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:58:42.000Z","msg":"上唔到大6打返落黎香港賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過佢地仲有好多逃稅既方法既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5b5d1508d1ad1eaeb6705a9ce8209f53280a28e","tid":1396093,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T04:27:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9daac50a255d6960f407367466d8f235a38db6e","tid":1396093,"uid":171684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:21:52.000Z","msg":"支那自己出爾反爾 抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b1490837d04d9a96984cbef04b093d9d05e571a","tid":1396093,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:26:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}